name: Money
description: Introducing the game's lifeblood: Coins! Because apparently, you can't buy happiness, but you can buy a digital horse head. Close enough, right?

name: Horse head
description: Upgrade your character's noggin to a majestic horse head! Embrace the whimsy of equine elegance as you gallop through adventures with newfound horsepower â€“ quite literally. Neigh-sayers, beware!

name: Regeneration
description: Experience the magic of self-repairing tissue with our Regeneration Upgrade! Watch in awe as your character effortlessly heals wounds, bruises, and even broken bones over time. Say goodbye to medkits and hello to a body that bounces back from any battle. Heal up, hero, and let your enemies marvel at your newfound resilience!

name: Resilience
description: Resilience: Because sometimes even the fiercest warriors need a little extra padding against life's unexpected punches. Laugh in the face of danger as this item turns bruises into mere love taps!

name: Empowerment
description: Empowerment: Because sometimes, even superheroes need a pep talk. Tap into your inner greatness and unleash the true hero within. Feel the power surge as you rise above the mundane and conquer the extraordinary. With great empowerment comes... well, you know the rest.
